--- Crowns ---
Crowns (Silver or White) Please read local anesthesia Your childs gums will be irritated and sore for the next three days. I highly recommend Childrens Ibuprofen or Tylenol for the first day. If there is throbbing pain, you may place a wrapped towel around a cold compress and place it on the cheek for 15 minutes and off for 15 minutes. Please continue to brush all your teeth.
